reviewText: As a big David Janssen fan I was looking forward to seeing something new and fresh even before The Fugitive came out.The quality of this DVD is very poor and makes it hard to watch.Someone should take this entire series and digitally remaster it!
Title: Richard Diamond, Private Eye: Picture of Fear/The Chess Player

reviewText: Service, shipping, product, description were excellent. The only problem I had was I wanted more than the one CD. It was that good! Many thanks for your excellent service!
Title: Richard Diamond, Private Eye: Picture of Fear/The Chess Player

reviewText: I would highly recommend to buy this DVD.It shows the real talent of the unforgettable actor David Janssen (incl. a little bio also).Remember: The Fugitive, the Original, this actor is outstanding.Transaction was great! Thank you!
summary: Richard Diamond, Private Eye - David Janssen
Title: Richard Diamond, Private Eye: Picture of Fear/The Chess Player

reviewText: My only complaint about this dvd is that there are only 2 episodes from the series on it. Both episodes excellent.Good story-lines. David Janssen in top form. An extra perk was the amusing Maxwell House presents intros.I had flashes of Jack Lemmon sitting in front of TV in The Apartment trying to find something to watch & only be able to find all the promo stuff :)BTW on this DVD is HOLLYWOOD REMEMBERS DAVID JANSSEN which is a great, all be it concise, profile of David Janssen, which I personally thoroughly enjoyed.
summary: Brought to you by Maxwell House
Title: Richard Diamond, Private Eye: Picture of Fear/The Chess Player
